page.title: 20DOMESDAY SURVEY,FLEETWOOD
page.content: The survey has been very interesting and challenging.We have learnt a great deal about our local area.The pupils have interviewed a number of people who have responded in a friendly and helpful way.Hopefully the skills gained as a result of the survey will benefit all pupils in the future. The Domesday Survey Editorial Board consisted of Mr.S.Coughlan,Gina O'Donnell,Lisa Coxall,Joanne Condron and Sally Waring.Other contributors were: Mrs M.Rae Pauline Hargreaves Duncan Baird Susan Jones Karen Beesley Fenella Machell Marie Bilsborrow Kathyrn McCarron Helen Cliff Louise Parker Joanne Cooper Juliet Reilly Lisa Croston Karen Robinson Helen Crowther Eleanor Taylor Angela Dunne Tim O'Sullivan Kerry White
